name: Lauterbach, Dr. Karl
tweet: {'id_': '1279891156915101703', 'raw_data': {'created_at': 'Sun Jul 05 21:33:25 +0000 2020', 'id': 1279891156915101703, 'id_str': '1279891156915101703', 'full_text': 'Ich sehe es genau anders.
